Mod Content:

Location - Banned Mare animated book on the wall near stairs

Where it leads - this teleport leads u to a new cell with every item in the game along with a small arena type area

Pros

New qasmoke like location better look more room 
ton of manniquins 

Cons 
the console command cocqasmoke probably dosnt work but if it does im awsome XD 
You need all DLC.

I sat here one day playing skyrim with around 20gig worth of mods new homes new places ect and every time i went to the qasmoke cell i felt like it it was quickly becoming an eyesore so i decided to make it newer and and an overall nice place to visit.
author: Azmerith
